{
  "texts": [
    "Silicon participant: \"As a 77-year-old woman with heart failure, some barriers I face in being physically active include (bullet points):",
    "• My physical limitations due to my condition and the need to avoid certain activities that could put too much stress on my heart.",
    "• Weather conditions, such as extreme heat or cold, can make it difficult for me to be active.",
    "Air quality and pollution can also be a barrier, especially if the air is not healthy enough to breathe.",
    "• Sometimes, I might be feeling tired or unwell and would need to take a rest."
  ]
}